data.description: Welcome to this wonderful three-bedroom, two and a half bath three level end unit condo in Spence Crossing. You'll find this home in the heart of Virginia Beach with close access to everything! The home is turn-key ready for new owners to create lasting memories with plenty of room for entertainment. Enjoy an abundance of natural lighting that creates an open airy experience. All while the community offers pool/clubhouse access, an exercise room, playgrounds, ground maintenance, trash pickup and water! Schedule your private showing today!
